Reviews.Title: As Described.  Good Siamese cable at a good price.
Reviews.Author: Josh Munford
Reviews.Content: I ran a continuity test between 1000 when I first got the reel.  Shield, core, and power were all good.  I then proceeded to pull 780' of it around all sorts of corners.  Checked continuity again on the runs and it was all good. Good product, good price.
